<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/54548932/answer/1925901730417213622" target="_blank"> 有哪些信、达、不雅的翻译？</a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/84dc60cabd8b4deb986d39d93d5386bf" target="_blank">@小王学长</a>：现象级美剧 <a class="RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1" href="https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=271626139&amp;content_type=Article&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=Breaking+Bad&amp;zhida_source=entity" target="_blank">Breaking Bad</a> 《绝命毒师》</div>
你可以将他翻译为：<br>《 Man ！沃尔特抗癌赛》<br>《吸 Ice 够》<br>《磅多粒一次卖够》<br>《神冰销将》<br>《胡闹厨房》<br>《货瘾忍者》<br>《冰和试剂》<br>《冰与货之歌》<br>《销麻暴利》<br>《亢吸王朝》<br>《吸吸粒的美丽传说》<br>《老人与嗨》<br>《沃氏特种冰》<br>《觅血冰城》<br>《嗨面堡煲》<br>《试冰突击》<br>《卖克白》<br>以及其他。</blockquote>
